The paper discusses the optimization of federated queries over linked data, which involves database management, artificial intelligence, distributed computing, information retrieval, and data mining. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.DB (Databases), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), cs.DL (Digital Libraries), and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
